<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:20:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>独家：中国奇瑞在西方竞争对手腾出的俄罗斯工厂组装汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-assembles-cars-russian-plants-vacated-by-western-rivals-2024-10-10/</link><description>五位知情人士告诉路透社，中国汽车制造商奇瑞已开始在俄罗斯组装汽车，并在大众和梅赛德斯等西方竞争对手腾出的三座工厂在该国销售。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-assembles-cars-russian-plants-vacated-by-western-rivals-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中概股盛会重启，关注周六</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-10-10/</link><description>Ankur Banerjee 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 04:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>赖表示，中国不能代表台湾，应与台北合作应对全球挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-has-no-right-represent-taiwan-should-work-with-taipei-global-challenges-2024-10-10/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德周四表示，中国无权代表台湾，但台湾愿意与北京合作应对气候变化等全球挑战，语气既坚定又和解。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 03:32:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-has-no-right-represent-taiwan-should-work-with-taipei-global-challenges-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国将开展全国人口变化调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hold-nationwide-survey-population-changes-2024-10-10/</link><description>中国国家统计局表示，在当局努力推动出生率下降之际，将从周四开始在全国范围内进行抽样调查，以“准确”监测人口变化，更好地规划经济和社会政策。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 03:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hold-nationwide-survey-population-changes-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市重拾涨势，交易员等待美国通胀测试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-10/</link><description>中国股市周四恢复涨势，因预期本周末财政官员的简报将带来预期的财政刺激措施，而美元在美国通胀报告公布前徘徊在两个月高点附近。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 02:55:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>韩国的尹恩惠和日本的石破将在东盟会议期间会面</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-yoon-japans-ishiba-meet-sidelines-asean-gathering-2024-10-10/</link><description>韩国总统尹锡烈和日本首相石破茂定于周四在老挝举行首次峰会，尹的办公室表示，邻国寻求深化安全和经济关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 01:59:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-koreas-yoon-japans-ishiba-meet-sidelines-asean-gathering-2024-10-10/</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，作为美国和解协议的一部分，道明银行面临 30 亿美元的罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/td-bank-faces-3-bln-penalties-growth-restrictions-us-settlement-wsj-reports-2024-10-09/</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，加拿大道明银行预计将支付约 30 亿美元的罚款，作为与美国监管机构和检察官就其未能适当监控贩毒集团洗钱行为达成和解的一部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 23:48:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/td-bank-faces-3-bln-penalties-growth-restrictions-us-settlement-wsj-reports-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国股市的现实检验，美元走高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-09/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 21:46:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国称台湾言论没有理由向中国施加军事压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-official-says-taiwan-speech-no-justification-china-military-pressure-2024-10-09/</link><description>美国周三表示，中国没有理由利用台湾一年一度的国庆讲话作为军事施压的借口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 16:36:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-official-says-taiwan-speech-no-justification-china-military-pressure-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>抗议要求改善条件的皮革工人在意大利遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/leather-workers-protesting-better-conditions-attacked-italy-2024-10-09/</link><description>意大利普拉托市的皮革制品工人工会周三表示，他们正在举行抗议活动，要求改善工作条件，但他们在守卫纠察线时遭到袭击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 13:49:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/leather-workers-protesting-better-conditions-attacked-italy-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，巴基斯坦将在上合组织峰会期间遏制中国的行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-curb-movement-chinese-nationals-during-sco-conference-say-sources-2024-10-09/</link><description>三名安全官员和一份内部安全说明称，巴基斯坦当局正在寻求在下周的上海合作组织会议期间限制中国公民的行动，因为激进组织针对中国公民构成安全风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 13:13:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-curb-movement-chinese-nationals-during-sco-conference-say-sources-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>伦敦证券交易所数据显示，本月外国资金正在撤离中国以外的亚洲股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-money-is-leaving-asian-equities-ex-china-this-month-lseg-data-shows-2024-10-09/</link><description>由于对股票估值过高和中东冲突的担忧促使投资者获利了结，外国资金本月正在离开亚洲股市（不包括中国）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:24:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-money-is-leaving-asian-equities-ex-china-this-month-lseg-data-shows-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体报道，欧盟对中国电动汽车做出裁决后，中欧团队将继续进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-eu-team-continue-talks-after-blocs-ruling-chinese-evs-state-media-reports-2024-10-09/</link><description>官方通讯社新华社周三援引知情人士的话报道称，中国最近与美国和欧盟就电动汽车贸易问题进行了“密集沟通”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-eu-team-continue-talks-after-blocs-ruling-chinese-evs-state-media-reports-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>日本最高外交官向中国王室提出有关刺伤和军事活动的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-looks-forward-new-atmosphere-with-new-japan-cabinet-minister-says-2024-10-09/</link><description>日本新任外相周三在自上周上任以来首次与中国外长王毅通电话时，对在华日本公民遭持刀袭击以及中国的军事活动表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 12:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-looks-forward-new-atmosphere-with-new-japan-cabinet-minister-says-2024-10-09/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉9月中国产电动汽车销量同比增长19.2%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-grow-192-yy-sept-2024-10-09/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周三的数据显示，美国汽车制造商特斯拉9月份中国制造的电动汽车销量同比增长19.2%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 11:15:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-grow-192-yy-sept-2024-10-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>